      "text": [
        " «يَمْضِي عَلَى صَلاَتِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1565 - Uqbah ibn Khalid asked Him (Imam Abu Abdullah (as)) about a man who was praying and another man called out to him, causing him to become distracted and respond to the person's request. What should he do?\nImam (as) said: \"He should continue with his prayer.\""
        ]
      }
